---
title: Cumin Roast Chicken with Patatas Bravas and Charred Courgettes
description: Holidays are over but today's recipe will transport you to Spain. Although it was actually inspired by Mimi's visit to a tapas restaurant in Dundee! Patatas bravas is the quintessential tapas dish, available all over Spain. Not everyone loves the casual, sharing business of tapas so we've given you plenty for a portion each alongside some delicious cumin roast chicken!
